        Constructor of task result.
        Parameters:
        resultId - Result Id, same as its associated task Id.
        subTasks - Subtasks to be stored in Space. First task is a successor task to be stored in Successor Task Queue, following by child ready tasks to be stored in Ready Task Queue.
        coarse - Coarse flag
        taskStartTime - Task start time.
        taskEndTime - Task end time.

        Process the result. Call from Space. Put Successor Task in the Successor Task Map, put Ready Task into the Ready Task Queue.
        Specified by:
        process in class Result
        Parameters:
        space - The Space implemetation in which the result is to be processed.
        runningTaskMap - The Running Task Map in the Computer Proxy, where the associated task is stored.
